OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,FThe chief inspector of Ofsted will say
OL,7,Fhe is serious about the watchdog
OL,8,F"doing better" as he launches a major
OL,9,Fconsultation into its future direction.
OL,11,FSir Martyn Oliver will pledge to put
OL,12,Fthe interests of disadvantaged
OL,13,Fchildren at the heart of any reforms
OL,14,Fand will say "nothing is off the
OL,15,Ftable" in the watchdog's "Big Listen"
OL,16,Fpublic consultation.
OL,18,FOfsted has come under greater scrutiny
OL,19,Fin the past year following the suicide
OL,20,Fof headteacher Ruth Perry.
