OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,FIn his first major speech since
OL,7,Fbecoming chief inspector, Sir Martyn
OL,8,Fwill tell school leaders that he wants
OL,9,Fthe Big Listen consultation to mark a
OL,10,Fnew chapter in the watchdog's
OL,11,Frelationship with the sector.
OL,13,FViews about Ofsted's work will be
OL,14,Fsought from parents, carers and
OL,15,Fprofessionals in the education and
OL,16,Fsocial care sectors as part of the 12-
OL,17,Fweek consultation, which opens on
OL,18,FFriday.
