OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,FSir Martyn will tell the annual
OL,7,Fconference of the Association of
OL,8,FSchool and College Leaders (ASCL) in
OL,9,FLiverpool: "We need to listen to
OL,10,Ffeedback, to criticism, to ideas for
OL,11,Fsmall changes and for big reforms.
OL,13,F"If your work, your children, your
OL,14,Fdecisions, your education or your care
OL,15,Fare impacted by what we do, we want to
OL,16,Fhear from you. Every voice will be
OL,17,Fheard, and nothing is off the table."
