OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,FHis comments come after a report by
OL,7,Fthe Education Select Committee in
OL,8,FJanuary called on the Department for
OL,9,FEducation (DfE) and Ofsted "to develop
OL,10,Fan alternative" to the single-word
OL,11,Fjudgments used to rate schools in
OL,12,FEngland.
OL,14,FRelations between Ofsted and teachers
OL,15,Fand school leaders have become
OL,16,F"extremely strained" and trust in the
OL,17,Finspectorate is "worryingly low", MPs
OL,18,Ffrom the cross-party group concluded.
OL,26,@qD@\OUrD@OO]xD@AOUxD@TO]yD@QOUyD@`O]
