OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,FAddressing hundreds of headteachers on
OL,7,FFriday morning, Sir Martyn, who took
OL,8,Fover as chief inspector in January,
OL,9,Fwill say: "I hope the steps I've taken
OL,10,Fin my first two months show you that
OL,11,FI'm serious.
OL,13,F"Serious about Ofsted doing better.
OL,14,FSerious about making a difference. And
OL,15,Fserious about working with the sector
OL,16,Fto make sure all children have the
OL,17,Fbest possible education, care, and
OL,18,Flife chances.'
OL,26,@qD@KOUuD@AOU
