OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,FFollowing the inquest into Mrs Perry's
OL,7,Fdeath, Sir Martyn delayed school
OL,8,Finspections until later on in January
OL,9,Fto ensure inspectors received mental
OL,10,Fhealth training.
OL,12,FThe watchdog has also published a
OL,13,Fpolicy on how inspections can be
OL,14,Fsuspended in exceptional circumstances
OL,15,F` including where the head requires
OL,16,Fsupport.
OL,18,FThe watchdog's Big Listen consultation
OL,19,Fwill ask a series of questions to help
OL,20,Fprovide a sense of direction for the
OL,21,Fchanges Ofsted could make.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/12
