OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,FIndependent organisations will also
OL,7,Fcarry out surveys and focus groups
OL,8,Fwith parents and professionals to
OL,9,Fgather their views on Ofsted.
OL,11,FLaunching the consultation, Sir Martyn
OL,12,Fwill say: "We want to see high
OL,13,Fstandards for all children, and
OL,14,Fpositive outcomes for all children.
OL,15,FThis is how we start to tackle
OL,16,Fdisadvantage as a society ` by opening
OL,17,Fnew doors, creating new opportunities
OL,18,Fand better life chances.
OL,26,@tD@KOU
