OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,F"We don't want disadvantage or
OL,7,Fvulnerability to be a barrier. Because
OL,8,Fif you get it right for the most
OL,9,Fdisadvantaged, you get it right for
OL,10,Feveryone. Ofsted has a crucial role to
OL,11,Fplay in making sure that happens, and
OL,12,Fpointing out when it doesn't."
OL,14,FOfsted will publish its conclusions
OL,15,Fand plans later this year after it has
OL,16,Fanalysed all the responses to the
OL,17,Fconsultation.
