OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,FGeoff Barton, general secretary of the
OL,7,FASCL, said: "We welcome the 'big
OL,8,Flisten' as an important step in
OL,9,Fresetting the broken relationship
OL,10,Fbetween Ofsted and the schools and
OL,11,Fcolleges it inspects.
OL,13,F"It is vital that the inspectorate
OL,14,Fwins back the confidence of leaders
OL,15,Fand teachers who at present regard it
OL,16,Fas unnecessarily harsh, punitive and
OL,17,Finconsistent.
OL,26,@oD@MOUuD@AOU
