OL,3,COfsted chief inspector 'serious' about
OL,4,Cwatchdog 'doing better'
OL,6,F"Sir Martyn Oliver has already
OL,7,Fsignalled a change of tone, and this
OL,8,Fhas been well received ` but the proof
OL,9,Fof the pudding is in this translating
OL,10,Fto a better and fairer system."
OL,12,FMr Barton added: "We have repeatedly
OL,13,Fcalled for the current system of
OL,14,Fgraded judgements ` where everything a
OL,15,Fschool does is reduced to a single
OL,16,Fphrase ` to be scrapped and replaced
OL,17,Fwith a narrative description which is
OL,18,Fmore informative for parents and more
OL,19,Fsupportive to schools that need
OL,20,Fadditional support.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@_O]tD@ROU
